---++++Example 1.4.1 - Description in Box 1.4.1 represented in SDD
d321 1
a321 1
<table bgcolor="#ddddff" border="0" width="100%" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="5" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111">
d323 1
